==Ancient Greek==

===Pronunciation===
*εὐαγγελίζω / euaggelizō / yoo-ang-ghel-id'-zo


===Verb===
'''εὐαγγελίζω'''

# To [[declare]], [[bring]] (declare, show) glad (good) tidings, [[preach]] (the gospel).

===Etymology===
*From [[εὖ]] {{GG|2095}} and [[ἄγγελος]] {{GG|32}}; to announce good news (“evangelize”) especially the gospel

